data.description: **Seller willing to provide concession** Nestled in the heart of Cibolo, this stunning 4-bedroom, 2 1/2-bathroom gem is your next dream home! Just a quick 15-minute drive from Randolph Air Force Base, major shopping areas, and grocery stores, convenience meets comfort in this prime location.  As you step inside, be captivated by the grandeur of vaulted ceilings and exquisite crown molding throughout the downstairs. The open floor plan welcomes you with a flood of natural light, creating a warm and inviting atmosphere.The kitchen, adorned with stainless steel appliances, becomes the heart of your morning routine as you savor a cup of coffee. Picture relaxing in the spacious living room, perfect for unwinding after a busy day. Retreat to the tranquility of the primary bedroom downstairs in the evenings, while family or guests enjoy the privacy of the upstairs game room and three additional bedrooms. This worry-free haven comes complete with a full sprinkler system, plumbing for a water softener, a brand-new split AC system featuring a preventative mold device, a new damper, and a sparkling new dishwasher. The well-maintained roof ensures peace of mind for years to come. Your new home awaits - a perfect blend of comfort, convenience, and contemporary living. Schedule your tour today and make this Cibolo sanctuary your own!
